Invocation Name: travel buddy
des: Travis helps you with the places you can visit all over the world. It helps you with cities, countries and any region as such. It doesn't take your location so your privacy is safe. It gives you suggestions in the order of how famous the place is. Hope you can visit all its suggestion. Plan your trip ahead with Travis!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
